metadata.name: CULTIVATE - SORCE VIAL [POWERED]
metadata.description:
The Sorce Energy Vial is the most potent creative force in the Metaverse, and powers all digital wearables and assets from Cultivate. 
Holders of a Sorce Energy Vial will be granted guaranteed access to minting the DR1VER Helmet, and unlocks future utility in the Cultivate universe.
